			<div type="transcription">
				<div type="original">
					<p>The original transcription is not available.</p>
				</div>
				<div type="translation">
					<pb facs="R 87-11 12 (11).jpg" n="2"/>
					<p><!--{{Ray Atherton}}, Arrest of [Professor Kantardjieff] in connection with <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-199" type="subject">anti-Semitic</term>
        <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-199" type="subject">demonstration </term>[sic], <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/727011/sofia.html">Sofia</placeName>, 4.4.1939, S. 2.</p>
      <p>Records of the Department of State relating to internal affairs of <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/732800/republic-of-bulgaria.html">Bulgaria</placeName>
        1910-1944, Washington 1982 (Mikrofilm-Edition): Dokument 874.4016/45--></p>
					<p>[...] There is no sympathy in <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/732800/republic-of-bulgaria.html">Bulgaria</placeName> for the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-199" type="subject">anti-Jewish demonstrations</term> of this organization
							‚<orgName ref="#ehri_dr_workers_of_the_new_bulgaria">Workers of New Bulgaria</orgName>‘, especially as there is no <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jewish</term> problem here, the total number of <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term> amounting to less than 55,000. The <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term> are not active in <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-983" type="subject">political</term> and public life; there are none among the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1077" type="subject">army</term> officers and almost none in civil service.
						Their sphere of activity is <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-924" type="subject">business</term>, <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-937" type="subject">industry</term> and small <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-933" type="subject">trades</term>, and there are very few <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term> in the liberal professions and <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-673" type="subject">arts</term>. The anti-Jewish <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-986" type="subject">propaganda</term> conducted by the ‚<orgName ref="#ehri_dr_workers_of_the_new_bulgaria">Workers of New Bulgaria</orgName>‘ is of foreign origin and is, it is believed, directly encouraged from <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/2921044/federal-republic-of-germany.html">Germany</placeName>.[...]</p>
